Comment: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I heard about it.
Comment: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it was really rough.
Comment: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like a weight got \Nlifted off of your shoulders?
Comment: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hở? Chuyện gì cơ?
Comment: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean my sister?
Comment: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Comment: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that was rough, too, though.
Comment: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Will you tell your sister congrats\Non finishing her exams for me?
Comment: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why would I?
Comment: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to give her a message from you?
Comment: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm happy to hear \Nyou say that. Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't think you'd thank me for {\i1}that{0}.
Comment: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't referring to your \Nlittle sister, though…
Comment: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that other little sister.
Comment: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Comment: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, would you like to come in?
Comment: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to drink more?
Comment: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. There are some \Ndays I just want to drink.
Comment: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Còn nữa, rượu còn giúp cuộc sống trơn tru hơn đó!
Comment: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's more often the \Nroot cause of problems, though.
Comment: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll listen \Nto what you have to say.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You won't listen to \Nme even when you're sober.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true! Now then…
Comment: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you wanna say?
Comment: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about us,\Nand what will happen with us in the future.
Comment: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Comment: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to let me in on all that?
Comment: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about you and me. And also about Mom.
Comment: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's what you meant.
Comment: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't sound like \Nsomething I want to hear.
Comment: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Comment: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want you to listen.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going home.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I will talk to Mom about \Nmy future and what I want.
Comment: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't get what I want,\NI don't want to have any regrets.
Comment: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to... at least make myself clear,
Comment: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,để chính bản thân em có thể chấp nhận được nó.
Comment: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So I guess that's your answer, then.
Comment: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine. You've \Ngrown a little, I guess.
Comment: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you want to say.\NIf you're serious about it, then I'll work with you.
Comment: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll work with me?
Comment: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's not the type of person\Nto change course very easily.
Comment: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll put in a good word \Nfor you when appropriate.
Comment: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, I don't know\Nif that will be effective or not.
Comment: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you should go there with the assumption\Nthat you won't be back here for awhile.
Comment: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Phải vậy nhỉ!
Comment: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:55.06,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only allowed to come here\Nbecause she was worried about Yukino.
Comment: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If Yukino goes home,\Nshe probably won't be set free again so easily.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,First, pack up your things.\NThen you'll need to get in touch with Mom.
Comment: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes… I'll do that.
Comment: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll have free use of this \Nplace for awhile. That okay?
Comment: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do what you want with it.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you pack up, too!
Comment: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't let you do that for me, too…
Comment: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally okay! I actually want you to let me help.\NI really like organizing things!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Comment: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the only thing \NI'm able to help you with…
Comment: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her do it.
Comment: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Free labor is hard to find nowadays.
Comment: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.\NWhy don't you go ahead and stay the night?
Comment: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be… asking too much?
Comment: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd love to!
Comment: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do some decluttering! I recently bought\Na ton of books on how to declutter!
Comment: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those books are the first thing\Nthat should be decluttered.
Comment: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the convenience store.
Comment: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,có ai cần mua gì không?
Comment: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you went to the convenience store.
Comment: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing feels a bit \Nlike a rendezvous, doesn't it?
Comment: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this more like an ambush?
Comment: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing.
Comment: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cigarette smoke, huh?
Comment: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drinking for quite some time, huh?
Comment: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, they wouldn't let me go home.
Comment: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost got pulled into \Ngoing at it all night.
Comment: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad I came home early.\NI was able to listen to what Yukino had to say.
Comment: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, that's just kind of surprising.
Comment: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Comment: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That you actually listened to her.
Comment: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Comment: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still her older sister, after all.
Comment: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what Yukino has chosen, then I will support\Nthat decision, whether it's the right one or not.
Comment: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's making the wrong \Nchoice, shouldn't you stop her?
Comment: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't listen to me.
Comment: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I don't care either way.
Comment: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because nothing will change.\NWhether it works out or she gives up.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody becomes an adult by giving up\Non various things like that, you know.
Comment: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see…
Comment: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là kinh nghiệm của chị nhỉ!
Comment: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I wonder!
Comment: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't matter here. We're \Ntalking about Yukino right now.
Comment: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the first time \Nshe's ever made herself clear.
Comment: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch over her too, Hikigaya.
Comment: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Comment: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I acted like a big sister again…
Comment: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try being \Nlike that all the time?
Comment: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I'm not like you.
Comment: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always acting like a big brother.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah… I am a big brother after all.
Comment: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see…
Comment: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to have an older brother like you.\NI wish I had one of those!
Comment: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey…You're being an \Nannoying drunk right now.
Comment: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm not drunk!
Comment: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Er… Can you make it home okay?
Comment: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so kind! A gentleman, even!
Comment: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a gentleman. I plan \Non going straight home.
Comment: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Comment: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I'd get drunk from that.
Comment: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something drunk people say.
Comment: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I'm really not drunk.
Comment: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can't get drunk.
Comment: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much alcohol I drink,\Na part of me always stays calm.
Comment: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even see what kind of face I'm making.
Comment: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I laugh and get wild,\NI feel like it's not actually me doing it.
Comment: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the same.
Comment: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling it right now.
Comment: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think the hard part starts now.\NJust guessing, though.
Comment: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Comment: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a whole lot better \Nthan it was before.
Comment: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she would never change.
Comment: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the same.
Comment: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling it right now.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get drunk.
Comment: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me!
Comment: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, s-sorry…
Comment: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you scare too easily!
Comment: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Comment: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the club?
Comment: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. For now, I mean…
Comment: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why do you have that blanket?
Comment: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Blanket? Oh you mean the one for my lap?
Comment: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for your lap, huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a different one before?
Comment: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You pay more attention \Nto me than I thought...
Comment: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no… N-not especially \Nor anything, I just…
Comment: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, why'd you buy a new blanket\Neven though you already have one?
Comment: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How many laps do you have? \NAre you a centipede?
Comment: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Comment: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought a magazine and this \Ncame with it! That's it!
Comment: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do that a lot, because I \Nrealized I have too many blankets
Comment: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't know what to do with them.
Comment: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right…
Comment: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, if our club continues for a little longer,\NI was thinking I'd leave it in the room…
Comment: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it continues, huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still locked.
Comment: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Yukinon hasn't come yet.
Comment: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the key.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? U-um, wait…
Comment: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikigaya.
Comment: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Comment: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get the key for our club room.
Comment: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yukinoshita already came \Nand took the key earlier.
Comment: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I'd call her.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't think you said that.
Comment: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cause you left before I said it!
Comment: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I went ahead and made tea… \NWould you like some?
Comment: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… About the other day...
Comment: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you finish the move okay?
Comment: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wouldn't go as far as \Nto call it "moving," though…
Comment: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuigahama was there to help me.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, not a problem! It was no big deal.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me out. Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Comment: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I borrowed a DVD, but the student council laptop\Nis too new and doesn't even play DVDs!
Comment: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Comment: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite small, but \Nit's a projector, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Comment: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it can even display \Nvideos off a smartphone.
Comment: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's expensive, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, get this!
Comment: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It came entirely out of the student council\Nbudget, which comes at zero personal cost to me!
Comment: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst\Nproduct demo sales presentation ever.
Comment: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, I'm gonna put the screen up!
Comment: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was great!
Comment: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, why were you \Nwatching a movie here?
Comment: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not a movie, it's a TV drama.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That part doesn't matter…
Comment: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching it for reference.
Comment: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I watched it in the student council room,\NI would seem like I'm slacking off.
Comment: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say about the fact\Nyou chose to watch it here?
Comment: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it at home!
Comment: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I follow the principle of not working\Noutside of designated hours!
Comment: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you mean by "reference?"
Comment: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a graduation \Nceremony this year, right?
Comment: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then something called a \Nthank-you party or something?
Comment: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The student council has \Nto manage all of that.
Comment: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the thank-you party.
Comment: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, a normal \Nthank-you party is fine,
Comment: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I think about the \None from when I graduated,
Comment: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make something \Nmore flashy for this one.
Comment: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.. And I think the graduates\Nwould be happy with it, too.
Comment: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you want the prom.
Comment: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You always just get it \NYukinoshita! You're so great!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro…? What's that?
Comment: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A promenade, otherwise known as a prom.
Comment: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, it's an abbreviation \Nfor a type of dance.
Comment: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In high schools overseas,\Nit's the last dance party of the school year.
Comment: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There was a scene like \Nthat in the drama, too!
Comment: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why not just do a normal one?\NWhy do you want to make it a prom?
Comment: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, I'm going to be the prom queen!
Comment: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Comment: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was in the drama, too.
Comment: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That scene where they were like
Comment: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"let's choose\Nthe hottest boy and girl in our year!" or whatever.
Comment: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For our grade, the prom king\Nwould undoubtedly be Hayama.
Comment: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's probably true!
Comment: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, Hayama will be the \Nking, and I'll be the qu-
Comment: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Hikigaya, this is totally unrelated,\Nbut are you going to get held back a year?
Comment: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Comment: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Comment: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be the same as spending a year\Nwaiting to retake university entrance exams right?
Comment: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And using your student discount\Nis always a great bargain, you know?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assign that future to me.\NBesides, I'd lose way more than I'd save.
Comment: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what if you help with \Nthe prom instead, then?
Comment: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of? Instead of what?
Comment: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you seriously going to hold a prom?
Comment: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it definitely can't happen \Neven if you start it now.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it looks like fun, \Nbut… it also looks difficult.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Comment: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Comment: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to do it… Do you \Nthink that's unacceptable?
Comment: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of acceptability,\Nbut more that it's not really doable.
Comment: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a multitude of reasons why,\Nbut… I mean, you understand that, right?
Comment: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the student council will \Ntry to do this on our own.
Comment: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, good decision… Huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you listening?
Comment: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So we're going to do it on our own.
Comment: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay. Alright then.
Comment: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you change your mind or gain an interest,\Ncome hang out in the student council room!
Comment: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always welcome!\NSo much that we won't let you go!
Comment: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants to run us ragged, doesn't she?
Comment: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Comment: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to do so much to hold a prom?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, because, I mean, I \Nwant to be prom queen…
Comment: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean in two years, right?
Comment: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well…
Comment: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta start laying the \Ngroundwork for that now.
Comment: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing that a prom is \Nheld two years from now,
Comment: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be chosen as queen\Neven if you don't lay any groundwork today.
Comment: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... What?!
Comment: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying there's no real reason\Nyou have to do this right now.
Comment: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even next year, there will be no problem…
Comment: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work!
Comment: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dù có đề nghị tổ chức vào năm sau, thì nó cũng không thể diễn ra.
Comment: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be forced to give up\Nbecause they'll say we won't have enough time.
Comment: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why no matter how difficult \Nit is, and even if it's a flop,
Comment: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to lay the foundations \Nfor my next move!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki…
Comment: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be done now.
Comment: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start now, we may be ready in time.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What and who are you doing this for?
Comment: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For myself, of course!
Comment: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you for your answer.
Comment: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's get started.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-? Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real gonna do it?
Comment: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gawd, Yukinoshita! I freakin' love you!
Comment: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on…
Comment: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was with the third-degree\Nyou just gave me? It was scary!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if you'd stop \Ndoing stuff like that!
Comment: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we have no choice\Nif that's what the president has decided.
Comment: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our job.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we will.
Comment: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I speak with you two?
Comment: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just did was on \Nmy own personal volition.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of forcing you to help.
Comment: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay. What do you mean?
Comment: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, well… this was not a decision\NI made as club president,
Comment: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't have the authority \Nto make you help.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, I would be grateful\Nto receive help from you two…
Comment: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply, even if it's on my own,
Comment: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to take responsibility for the prom\Nand see it through to completion.
Comment: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather…
Comment: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we're free to participate or not?
Comment: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hikki.
Comment: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinon is saying that she wants to try\Nto do this on her own, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be done now…\NIf we start now, we may be ready in time.
Comment: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe… That applies to me, too.
Comment: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Comment: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a proper start.
Comment: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if you two would watch over me.
Comment: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't say a word. But promise me,\Nyou will absolutely not overexert yourself.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you need manpower \Nthen you have to call us.
Comment: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not as the Service Club,\Nyou can call us as your friends.
Comment: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you when that happens.
Comment: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I promise I will.
Comment: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Sounds good to \Nme! How about you, Hikki?
Comment: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Same.
Comment: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I making a mistake?
Comment: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this sounds fine. No idea, though.
Comment: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You never say anything helpful.
Comment: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, for the most part!
Comment: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, thanks for your help, Yukino!
Comment: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she just call you?
Comment: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to this.
Comment: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you please come\Nto the student council room starting tomorrow?
Comment: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I don't mind.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Act like you didn't see it.
Comment: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinon.
Comment: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking this coat with you?
Comment: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't need it.
Comment: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Comment: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Comment: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Comment: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have some mineral water left.
Comment: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually realized it a long time ago.
Comment: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a place that I couldn't get into,
Comment: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and though I stand in front of \Nthat door time and time again,
Comment: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling that \NI shouldn't disturb it.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is peek in through \Na crack and eavesdrop…
Comment: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I realized it a long time ago.
Comment: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to go there.\NI wanted nothing more than that.
Comment: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, honestly…
Comment: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,That Key Was Never Handled\NUntil Today.
Comment: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted anything genuine.
Comment: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.77,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,You like chick flick movies \Nlike that, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:42.06,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it a relief \Nthat I prefer chick flicks?
Comment: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:45.23,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Women who say they prefer\NHollywood action blockbusters
Comment: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.86,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,are only saying that to \Nappease their boyfriends.
Comment: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:47.73,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true?
Comment: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.32,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,In nine cases out of ten, yes.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.20,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Comment: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.87,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Okay. But evil women always \Npull moves like that to-
Comment: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.37,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Wait, were you just hitting on me?
Comment: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.92,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Did you say that because you were going \Nto invite me on a movie date after this?
Comment: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:03.00,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I ruined it.
Comment: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.71,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Seriously? There's no point now…
